***************************
  Name : Alshakh
  HW 2 : ISS 2011
    It draws roughly the ISS as it's in 2011. It offers two draw options and two
    projection options. 
  Time : About 14 hrs.
***************************

Build and Run:
    make clean;make run
Usage :
    Arrows  to see the scene from different angles
    w/s     to traverse in param menu
    a/d     to change value of params
    h       to hide/show axes and params
    1,2,3,4 to rotate solar panels
